INFO.name: QUERY
INFO.value: SELECT distinct asa_ous.asa_project_code AS "Project code", asa_science.source_name AS "Source name", asa_science.ra AS "RA", asa_science.dec AS "Dec", asa_science.gal_longitude AS "Galactic longitude", asa_science.gal_latitude AS "Galactic latitude", asa_science.band_list AS "Band", to_number(asa_science.spatial_resolution) AS "Spatial resolution", asa_science.frequency_resolution AS "Frequency resolution", concat(concat(case when asa_science.ant_main_num > 0 then '12m' else '' end, case when asa_science.ant_aca_num > 0 then '7m' else '' end), case when asa_science.ant_tp_num > 0 then 'TP' else '' end) as "Array", (case when asa_science.is_mosaic = 'Y' then 'mosaic' else '' end) as "Mosaic", asa_science.int_time AS "Integration", (case when asa_delivery_status.release_date is null then null when aqua_ous_flag.flag_name is null then to_char(asa_delivery_status.release_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD') else '3000-01-01' end) AS "Release date", asa_science.frequency_support AS "Frequency support", asa_science.velocity_resolution AS "Velocity resolution", asa_science.pol_products AS "Pol products", to_char(asa_science.start_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') AS "Observation date", asa_project.pi_name AS "PI name", asa_science.schedblock_name as "SB name", asa_project.coi_name AS "Proposal authors", min(asa_energy.sensitivity_10kms) AS "Line sensitivity (10 km/s)", asa_science.cont_sensitivity_bandwidth AS "Continuum sensitivity", asa_science.pwv AS "PWV", asa_ous.group_ous_uid as "Group ous id", asa_ous.member_ous_uid as "Member ous id", asa_science.asdm_uid AS "Asdm uid", asa_project.title AS "Project title", asa_project.type AS "Project type", asa_science.scan_intent AS "Scan intent", asa_science.fov AS "Field of view", asa_science.spatial_scale_max AS "Largest angular scale", asa_delivery_status.qa2_passed AS "QA2 Status", (select count(distinct asab.bibcode) from alma.asa_project_bibliography asab where project_code = alma.asa_ous.asa_project_code) AS "Pub", asa_project.science_keyword AS "Science keyword", asa_project.scientific_category AS "Scientific category", asa_ous.asa_project_code FROM alma.asa_science inner join alma.asa_science rawdata on rawdata.parent_dataset_id = asa_science.dataset_id inner join alma.aqua_execblock on rawdata.asdm_uid = aqua_execblock.execblockuid inner join alma.asa_ous on asa_science.asa_ous_id = asa_ous.asa_ous_id inner join alma.asa_project on rawdata.project_code = asa_project.code left outer join alma.asa_project_bibliography on rawdata.project_code = asa_project_bibliography.project_code left outer join alma.asa_delivery_asdm_ous on rawdata.asdm_uid = asa_delivery_asdm_ous.asdm_uid left outer join alma.asa_delivery_status on asa_delivery_asdm_ous.deliverable_name = asa_delivery_status.delivery_id inner join alma.asa_energy on asa_science.dataset_id = asa_energy.asa_dataset_id left join alma.AQUA_OUS_FLAG on AQUA_OUS_FLAG.ous_status_entity_id = asa_ous.asa_ous_id and AQUA_OUS_FLAG.FLAG_NAME = 'QA3_ONGOING' WHERE (1=1) AND asa_science.product_type = 'MOUS' AND lower(asa_ous.asa_project_code) not like '%.csv' AND ( asa_science.DEC BETWEEN -49.634566666666665 AND -49.301233333333336 AND asa_science.RA BETWEEN 196.10720239206836 AND 196.62012260793165 AND (asin(sqrt((-0.623549 - asa_science.cx) * (-0.623549 - asa_science.cx) + (-0.183091 - asa_science.cy) * (-0.183091 - asa_science.cy) + (-0.760042 - asa_science.cz) * (-0.760042 - asa_science.cz)) / 2.0) < 0.001454)) AND (asa_delivery_status.release_date < to_date('2019-03-16', 'YYYY-mm-dd')) AND (lower(ASA_SCIENCE.scan_intent) LIKE '%target%') GROUP BY asa_ous.asa_project_code, asa_science.source_name, asa_science.ra, asa_science.dec, asa_science.gal_longitude, asa_science.gal_latitude, asa_science.band_list, asa_science.spatial_resolution, asa_science.frequency_resolution, asa_science.ant_main_num, asa_science.ant_aca_num, asa_science.ant_tp_num, asa_science.is_mosaic, asa_science.int_time, asa_delivery_status.release_date, aqua_ous_flag.flag_name, asa_science.frequency_support, asa_science.velocity_resolution, asa_science.pol_products, asa_science.start_date, asa_project.pi_name, asa_science.schedblock_name, asa_project.coi_name, asa_science.cont_sensitivity_bandwidth, asa_science.pwv, asa_ous.group_ous_uid, asa_ous.member_ous_uid, asa_science.asdm_uid, asa_project.title, asa_project.type, asa_science.scan_intent, asa_science.fov, asa_science.spatial_scale_max, asa_delivery_status.qa2_passed, asa_project.science_keyword, asa_project.scientific_category, asa_science.footprint ORDER BY "Release date" asc

FIELD.name: Project code
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: OUS Project Code

FIELD.name: Source name
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Name of the source as registered in the ASDM. Partial matches through wildcards (?, *), and boolean OR expressions ("|"), can be used.

FIELD.name: RA
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Right Ascension of the field pointing.

FIELD.name: Dec
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Declination of the field pointing.

FIELD.name: Galactic longitude
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Galactic longitude of the observation for RA/Dec. Estimated using PyEphem and RA/Dec.

FIELD.name: Galactic latitude
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Galactic latitude of the observation for RA/Dec. Estimated using PyEphem and RA/Dec.

FIELD.name: Band
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Space delimited list of bands

FIELD.name: Frequency resolution
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Estimated frequency resolution from all the spectral windows, using median values of channel widths.

FIELD.name: Integration
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Aggregated integration time for the field in the ASDM.

FIELD.name: Frequency support
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: All frequency ranges used by the field

FIELD.name: Velocity resolution
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Estimated velocity resolution from all the spectral windows, from frequency resolution.

FIELD.name: Pol products
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Polarisation products provided.

FIELD.name: PI name
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: case-insensitive partial match over the full PI name. Wildcards can be used

FIELD.name: SB name
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Name of the Scheduling Block used as a template for executing the ASDM containing this Field.

FIELD.name: Proposal authors
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Full name of CoIs .

FIELD.name: Continuum sensitivity
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Estimated noise in the aggregated continuum bandwidth. Note this is an indication only, it does not include the effects of flagging or dynamic range limitations.

FIELD.name: PWV
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Estimated precipitable water vapour from the XML_CALWVR_ENTITIES table.

FIELD.name: Group ous id
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Group OUS ID

FIELD.name: Member ous id
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Member OUS ID

FIELD.name: Asdm uid
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: UID of the ASDM containing this Field.

FIELD.name: Project title
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Case-insensitive search over the project title

FIELD.name: Project type
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Project type.

FIELD.name: Scan intent
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Scan intent list for the observed field.

FIELD.name: Field of view
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Field of view (arcsec). Estimated from the frequency and antennas

FIELD.name: Largest angular scale
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Due to the fact that radio antennas can not be placed infinitely close, measurements do have a smallest separation which translates into a maximal angular distance beyond which features can not be resolved reliably any more. Adding observations with the ALMA Total Power array can add those missing largest scales.

FIELD.name: QA2 Status
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Quality Assessment 2 status: does the Member / Group OUS fulfil the PI's requirements?

FIELD.name: ASA_PROJECT_CODE
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: OUS Project Code
